Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.00,0:00:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名琴美妙的音色喚來了重重事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.90,0:00:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生在音樂世家的橫禍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.40,0:00:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以意想不到的態勢急速蔓延
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.10,0:00:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看清真相的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.50,0:00:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去是小孩 頭腦却是大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.10,0:00:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字是名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.80,0:01:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應設樂蓮希小姐的邀請
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.60,0:02:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們造訪了設樂調一朗先生的公館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.90,0:02:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓮希小姐拜托我們幫忙調查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.30,0:02:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圍繞在名琴——斯特拉迪瓦裏周圍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.40,0:02:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從前年開始發生的一連串詭异的事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.90,0:02:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而剛登門片刻  附樓便火舌繚繞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.70,0:02:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在附樓中小憩的弦三朗先生就此一去不復返
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.40,0:02:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個烟頭是誰抽的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.50,0:02:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來不像是小五郎叔叔的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.10,0:02:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個牌子是弦三朗爺爺抽的烟吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.80,0:02:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麽說的話好像弦三朗先生來過這裏一次再去附樓的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.40,0:02:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是這樣的話  這個恐怕是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.30,0:02:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小弟弟  你上哪兒去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.20,0:02:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.80,0:02:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是事故  是殺人事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.50,0:02:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且如果我的推理沒錯的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.70,0:02:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個被襲擊的就是……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.60,0:03:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯特拉迪瓦裏小提琴的不和諧音 間奏曲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.40,0:03:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.80,0:03:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說這次的火灾是故意縱火嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.50,0:03:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起火原因是在床上吸烟  火源就在這個烟灰缸附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.50,0:03:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  你看這個烟蒂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.50,0:03:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後這個是弦三朗先生剛才在主樓抽的烟蒂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.70,0:03:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個牌子的烟  沒什麽特別的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.60,0:03:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有齒痕  你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.90,0:03:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔也有這樣的習慣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.00,0:03:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叼著香烟做事和說話的時候就會不知不覺地咬住烟嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.10,0:03:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是這個烟蒂却沒有齒痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.10,0:03:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不覺得奇怪嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.90,0:03:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.70,0:03:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爲了把火灾僞裝成是因爲床上吸烟而自然引起的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.60,0:03:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某個人故意先吸了幾口烟再放火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.40,0:03:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想這麽說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.20,0:04:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  這個房間的門只有從裏面才能上鎖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.30,0:04:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人要怎麽離開現場啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.70,0:04:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯案手法你也想到了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.50,0:04:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  還沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.10,0:04:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼就是小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.40,0:04:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主樓留下的烟蒂也許只是偶然咬了一下而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.20,0:04:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  弦三朗先生最不喜歡別人整理自己的房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.40,0:04:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏連一根咬過的烟頭都找不到才奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.30,0:04:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一點都不奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.90,0:04:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦三朗先生離開房間的時候都會把垃圾拿出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.70,0:04:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來到底是怎麽回事  你們突然沖出房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.40,0:04:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是這個小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.00,0:04:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.80,0:04:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算每次都把垃圾扔出去的話還是很奇怪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.80,0:04:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡覺前連抽幾根烟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.50,0:04:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  這是常有的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.70,0:04:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是在抽最後一根的時候不知不覺睡著了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.40,0:05:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此  但就這樣結案行嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.00,0:05:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這說不定是連續殺人事件啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.20,0:05:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.90,0:05:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又開始胡說八道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.50,0:05:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.90,0:05:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,30年前被强盜殺死的彈二朗(danjirou)先生的首字母是D
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.70,0:05:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩年前從樓梯上摔下的永美(emi)的首字母是E
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.40,0:05:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年前從陽臺上摔下的降人(furuto)先生是F
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.50,0:05:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後今天去世的弦三朗(genzaburou)先生是G
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.00,0:05:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D E F G
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.10,0:05:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是英文字母的排列
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.90,0:05:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將這些人的死串連在一塊兒的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.90,0:05:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個家的主人設樂調一朗先生的生日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.50,0:05:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許這個小鬼說的沒錯  是有某種聯繫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.10,0:05:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.60,0:05:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DEFG的話下一個就輪到名字首字母是H的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.10,0:05:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓮希(hasuki)小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.70,0:05:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  只留她一個人太危險了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.50,0:06:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽  下一個被攻擊的就是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.90,0:06:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麽可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.40,0:06:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是根據字母的順序來的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.10,0:06:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麽說的話從爸爸彈二朗開始的確是按DEFG的順序
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.20,0:06:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是巧合啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.90,0:06:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.10,0:06:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是今晚的安魂曲要怎麽辦呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.20,0:06:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安魂曲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.90,0:06:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們設樂家每次有親人去世的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.90,0:06:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都會有家人爲其演奏安魂曲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.50,0:06:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年是弦三朗先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.80,0:06:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且老爺和夫人那個樣子也無法演奏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.90,0:06:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.20,0:06:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽還是我來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.60,0:06:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾位也一起留下來嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.30,0:06:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽賀響輔的現場演奏可是很難聽到的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.80,0:06:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.90,0:06:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  樂器大部分都放在附樓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.70,0:06:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的只有鋼琴和那個……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.60,0:06:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯特拉迪瓦裏就不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.10,0:07:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的手會發抖的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.70,0:07:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽  就用我的小提琴吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.70,0:07:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我去拿我車上用慣的小提琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.70,0:07:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然比不過300年前製作的名琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.30,0:07:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那可是我父親留給我的唯一遺物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.70,0:07:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,論音色不相上下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.90,0:07:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想用了那把名琴又發生什麽不吉利的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.00,0:07:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說把那把琴拿出來的話絢音嬸嬸會不高興的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.70,0:07:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.10,0:07:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人好像把兒子降人少爺和那把琴視爲一體了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.30,0:07:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在去世之前降人少爺在老爺面前彈奏的就是那把名琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.90,0:07:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以自從那天以來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.40,0:07:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伴隨淩晨零時的鐘聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.50,0:08:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事調一朗先生知道嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.90,0:08:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.90,0:08:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲保管室就在老爺和夫人的房間中間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.00,0:08:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸的身影至今一定仍然深深鐫刻在奶奶的心中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.40,0:08:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽就請各位賞聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.80,0:08:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃爾夫岡·阿瑪迪烏斯·莫扎特所作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.10,0:08:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安魂曲第二部分 K·626
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.70,0:09:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.40,0:09:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,響輔叔叔他可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.20,0:09:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以德國音樂大學首席小提琴手的身份畢業的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.70,0:09:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爲什麽響輔先生把窗打開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.50,0:09:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是爲了讓爺爺奶奶都能聽到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.80,0:09:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樓上就是奶奶的臥室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.00,0:09:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個老奶奶的房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.10,0:09:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是通過保管室與爺爺的房間相連的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.00,0:09:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果從裏面上鎖的話就不能由保管室進入了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.60,0:09:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走廊裏的門可以用管家的主鑰匙打開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.20,0:09:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是夫妻臥室却是分開的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.00,0:09:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲爺爺的烟癮很重  而奶奶討厭烟味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.70,0:10:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到得了肺癌之後才戒烟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.40,0:10:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.60,0:10:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果老爺爺去世後誰來繼承那把昂貴的小提琴呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.80,0:10:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是弦三朗爺爺  可是現在是奶奶吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.30,0:10:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道爺爺是怎麽想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.00,0:10:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我更希望能够傳給響輔叔叔這樣的天才音樂家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.60,0:10:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的柯南  安靜一點聽啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.90,0:10:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.80,0:11:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才難道是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.80,0:11:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.80,0:11:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快叫救護車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.20,0:11:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.70,0:11:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老奶奶的名字叫絢音(Ayane)首字母是A
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.90,0:11:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.60,0:11:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都別想得到它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.00,0:11:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.30,0:11:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保管室在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.90,0:11:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右邊最裏面的一間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.10,0:12:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保管室的門從裏面上了鎖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.60,0:12:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且打開的窗邊還放著椅子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.90,0:12:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是自殺嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.80,0:12:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真是死神啊  毛利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.70,0:12:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只是巧合啦  目暮警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.80,0:12:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.70,0:12:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到哪里都會被捲入事件之中這正是偵探的本能啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.50,0:12:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才希望你老老實實呆在家裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.90,0:12:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,案發時間是半夜0點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.30,0:12:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地點是三樓的窗口  那是死者的臥室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.00,0:12:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候你在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.40,0:12:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在這間臥室樓下的房間裏與大家一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.30,0:12:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽響輔先生演奏安魂曲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.90,0:12:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安魂曲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.60,0:12:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  好像是設樂家的傳統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.70,0:13:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被燒死的弦三朗是三弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.60,0:13:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長子是調一朗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.20,0:13:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,30年前過世的次子彈二朗的兒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.80,0:13:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是剛才提到的響輔先生吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.20,0:13:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你知道絢音女士自殺的動機了嗎  名偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.10,0:13:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個還不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.80,0:13:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  恐怕就是那把小提琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.60,0:13:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是這裏的管家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.20,0:13:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之請先到絢音太太的房間裏來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.90,0:13:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這 這是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.80,0:13:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯特拉迪瓦裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.70,0:13:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道又有强盜入室  纏鬥中絢音太太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.20,0:13:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是這間房間的門明明是鎖著的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.00,0:13:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有搏鬥的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.70,0:13:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有任何人出入的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.50,0:13:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是夫人打開盒子前琴已經被什麽人弄壞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.90,0:13:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才受了刺激
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.70,0:13:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  只不過是損壞了一件樂器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.20,0:13:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您不知道嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.00,0:13:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是價值數億日元的傳說中的名琴啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.50,0:13:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且在絢音太太的心裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.30,0:14:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這把琴就好比已故的兒子降人的化身一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.50,0:14:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦發現這把琴被毀說不定真會有跳樓的衝動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.40,0:14:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.10,0:14:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.70,0:14:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想是那個老奶奶她自己摔壞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.70,0:14:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這小鬼又來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.50,0:14:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己摔的  爲什麽這麽說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.20,0:14:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊  這張桌子上有一處嶄新的傷痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.40,0:14:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是老奶奶掄起琴砸到桌子上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.30,0:14:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  又不是什麽都不懂的警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.30,0:14:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絢音太太怎麽會弄壞一把那麽珍貴的名琴呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.90,0:14:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是這麽想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.20,0:14:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這把琴是真品的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.60,0:14:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.00,0:14:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看啊  小提琴裏貼著的標簽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.30,0:14:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那標志上寫著G·A
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.40,0:14:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是安東尼奧·斯特拉迪瓦裏製作的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.90,0:14:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,縮寫應該是A·S才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.00,0:15:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麽會知道得那麽清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.50,0:15:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是以前新一哥哥告訴我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.00,0:15:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個偵探小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.00,0:15:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麽說來新一他好像對小提琴知道得特別清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.30,0:15:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲福爾摩斯也拉小提琴的關係吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.40,0:15:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽  這個G·A到底是什麽意思呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.90,0:15:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是製作這個複製品的人想開個玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.40,0:15:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用自己的縮寫字母來模仿真品的簽名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.60,0:15:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以模仿斯特拉迪瓦裏而出名的複製品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.70,0:15:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在以前就多得數不勝數
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.00,0:15:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你們看  在標簽下方寫著Made in Germany
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.30,0:15:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,100%的仿真品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.20,0:15:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.20,0:15:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我提到過的響輔先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.50,0:15:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來是哪幾個人在樓下的房間裏聽安魂曲的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.10,0:15:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  小蘭和這個小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.80,0:15:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有蓮希小姐和管家太太共5人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.90,0:15:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在演奏中發現絢音太太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.70,0:16:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是爲什麽奶奶會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.90,0:16:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,響輔叔叔好不容易才把她救了出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.30,0:16:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爲什麽還要自殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.20,0:16:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.70,0:16:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.60,0:16:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火灾時老奶奶沒能逃出來  是響輔先生和柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.70,0:16:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是真搞不懂啊  爲什麽要把複製品砸壞呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.80,0:16:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是一直都以爲是真品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.30,0:16:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忽然發現原來是複製品所以就一怒之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.50,0:16:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.30,0:16:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爺特地把真品拿去鑒定過幷留有鑒定標識的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.90,0:16:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這琴盒倒是真品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.90,0:16:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是這個啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.70,0:16:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.80,0:16:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏在床頭的窗簾裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.10,0:16:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絢音那傢夥  這麽粗魯地對待它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.20,0:16:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是安東尼奧·斯特拉迪瓦裏的標志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.60,0:16:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這應該是真的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.00,0:16:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粗看起來我也這麽認爲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.30,0:16:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不然就讓我拉一曲看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.00,0:17:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.60,0:17:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都這麽認爲的話那肯定是真的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.30,0:17:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此那把琴又是怎麽回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.30,0:17:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定是爲了給大家一個驚喜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.50,0:17:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外買了一把斯特拉迪瓦裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.50,0:17:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果却發現是個複製品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.60,0:17:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.80,0:17:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在丈夫發現自己浪費了大筆金錢之前自殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.10,0:17:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就說得通了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.00,0:17:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.60,0:17:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我進入房間的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.90,0:17:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,檢查過床可是什麽都沒發現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.30,0:17:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是誰偷偷地用複製品換下了斯特拉迪瓦裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.00,0:17:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在又把它還回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.70,0:17:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在我們之後進入這房間的某人出于某種目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.30,0:17:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.40,0:17:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.00,0:17:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要調查一下琴上的指紋說不定就知道是誰幹的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.10,0:17:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過琴上早就沾滿了我的指紋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.30,0:17:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的應該也不少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.00,0:17:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天中午爲了準備調一朗叔叔的生日宴會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.10,0:17:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在給斯特拉迪瓦裏校音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.80,0:17:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個房間裏嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.40,0:17:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.40,0:18:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後就把蓮希叫到這裏來把琴交給了她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.80,0:18:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.40,0:18:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這里拉了一小會兒  所以我的指紋也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.50,0:18:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時其他人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.10,0:18:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我一個人  響輔叔叔出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.80,0:18:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶說爲了不影響我們就到花園散步去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.90,0:18:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨後給來訪的毛利先生他們看了斯特拉迪瓦裏以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.70,0:18:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附樓就著火了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.10,0:18:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就把放在桌子上的斯特拉迪瓦裏放到保管室裏去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.40,0:18:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麽說來你們任何人都有可能調換小提琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.60,0:18:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是警官  誰換了琴又有什麽關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.50,0:18:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真品好好地回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.60,0:18:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定是這個小鬼根本沒好好找就在那裏胡說八道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.50,0:18:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是這起事件很奇怪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.00,0:18:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽地方奇怪了  這房間是密室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.40,0:18:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那保管室的門也上了鎖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.40,0:18:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且開著的窗邊還放著椅子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.30,0:18:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不管怎麽看都是自殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.00,0:19:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個房間有備用鑰匙嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.20,0:19:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了夫人自己的鑰匙以外就只有我身上的主鑰匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.10,0:19:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官  鑰匙已經在遺體的持有品中發現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.70,0:19:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.60,0:19:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧  根本不是什麽連續殺人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.30,0:19:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連續殺人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.20,0:19:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.80,0:19:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個小鬼說把30年前到現在陸續死去的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.10,0:19:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姓名按縮寫排列的話就是D E F G
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.60,0:19:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是火灾中去世的弦三朗先生是G
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.50,0:19:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨後跳樓自盡的絢音太太是A
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.30,0:19:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說沒有任何關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.10,0:19:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定是音階
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.00,0:19:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DEFGA……哆來咪是意大利語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.30,0:19:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用英語字母表示的話就是CDEFGAB
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.50,0:19:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有C大調什麽的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.00,0:19:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  那麽下一個字母就是B
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.70,0:19:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是名字以B開頭的人……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.00,0:20:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,津曲紅生(Benio)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.80,0:20:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下去的B就是指我了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.60,0:20:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麽說的話30年前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.50,0:20:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛開始在這裏工作的時候老爺說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.00,0:20:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你也是我們家人的話就正好是個完整的音階
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.40,0:20:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.50,0:20:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從調一朗的C開始  CDEFGAB就全了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.00,0:20:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這麽說過嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.10,0:20:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  我們還需要進一步調查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.20,0:20:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請各位待在自己的房間裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.10,0:20:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官  發現了被害人的脚趾紋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.70,0:20:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是下定决心直接踩上窗臺就跳了下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.60,0:20:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在跳樓之前一點也沒有猶豫啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.50,0:20:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官  這是自殺啦  而且這是密室啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.70,0:20:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,密室啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.50,0:20:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麽說的話弦三朗被燒死的房間也是密室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.60,0:20:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起火之前大家都在附樓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.30,0:20:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這4個人都有可能放火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.30,0:21:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨後這個房間也是密室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.10,0:21:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有什麽辦法的 一定會有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.40,0:21:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.30,0:21:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊  就在窗戶上面的那個透明的方形的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.10,0:21:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽啊 是透明膠帶嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.50,0:21:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右邊也有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.00,0:21:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小五郎叔叔讓我一定要問問清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.40,0:21:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尸體的周圍有沒有什麽可疑的東西一起掉下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.80,0:21:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麽說的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.60,0:21:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.60,0:21:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去像是筷子的尖端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.60,0:21:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們找到了一個被燒焦的盒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.70,0:21:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  好像可以放兩根棒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.60,0:22:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麽說盒子裏面是空的是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.70,0:22:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.70,0:22:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要使用這個就有可能殺害絢音太太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.60,0:22:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的就是密室的問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.20,0:22:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊  原來是這麽回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.40,0:22:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是還有一件事弄不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.30,0:22:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爲什麽那人要堅持那樣做呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.10,0:24:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  要解開謎團爲什麽需要斯特拉迪瓦裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.20,0:24:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一件事弄不明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.90,0:24:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.30,0:24:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT CONAN
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:25.80,0:24:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯特拉迪瓦裏小提琴的不和諧音 尾聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:45.50,0:24:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT Conan’s HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:47.50,0:24:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對樂感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:49.30,0:24:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:49.90,0:24:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不看絕對…不行～哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:52.40,0:24:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你開玩笑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:53.50,0:24:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要你管
